    },
    "innerText": "8. Vattakkhandhako"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Āgantukavattakathāvaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "357"
      },
      ". Vattakkhandhake ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "pattharitabba"
      },
      "nti ātape pattharitabbaṃ. Pāḷiyaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "abhivādāpetabbo"
      },
      "ti vandanatthāya vassaṃ pucchanena navako sayameva vandatīti vuttaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Nilloketabbo"
      },
      "ti oloketabbo."
    ],
    "innerText": "357. Vattakkhandhake pattharitabbanti ātape pattharitabbaṃ. Pāḷiyaṃ abhivādāpetabboti vandanatthāya vassaṃ pucchanena navako sayameva vandatīti vuttaṃ. Nilloketabboti oloketabbo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Āgantukavattakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Āvāsikavattakathāvaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "359"
      },
      ". ‘‘Yathābhāga’’nti ṭhapitaṭṭhānaṃ anatikkamitvā mañcapīṭhādiṃ papphoṭetvā pattharitvā upari paccattharaṇaṃ datvā dānampi senāsanapaññāpanamevāti dassento āha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘papphoṭetvā hi pattharituṃ pana vaṭṭatiyevā’’"
      },
      "ti."
    ],
    "innerText": "359. ‘‘Yathābhāga’’nti ṭhapitaṭṭhānaṃ anatikkamitvā mañcapīṭhādiṃ papphoṭetvā pattharitvā upari paccattharaṇaṃ datvā dānampi senāsanapaññāpanamevāti dassento āha ‘‘papphoṭetvā hi pattharituṃ pana vaṭṭatiyevā’’ti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Āvāsikavattakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Anumodanavattakathāvaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "362"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pañcame nisinne"
      },
      "ti anumodanatthāya nisinne. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na mahātherassa bhāro hotī"
      },
      "ti anumodakaṃ āgametuṃ na bhāro. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ajjhiṭṭhova āgametabbo"
      },
      "ti attanā ajjhiṭṭhehi bhikkhūhi anumodanteyeva nisīditabbanti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "362.Pañcame nisinneti anumodanatthāya nisinne. Na mahātherassa bhāro hotīti anumodakaṃ āgametuṃ na bhāro. Ajjhiṭṭhova āgametabboti attanā ajjhiṭṭhehi bhikkhūhi anumodanteyeva nisīditabbanti attho."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Anumodanavattakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Bhattaggavattakathāvaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "364"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Manussānaṃ"
      },
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "parivisanaṭṭhāna"
      },
      "nti yattha antovihārepi manussā saputtadārā āvasitvā bhikkhū netvā bhojenti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Āsanesu satī"
      },
      "ti nisīdanaṭṭhānesu ",
      " santesu. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Idaṃ, bhante, āsanaṃ ucca"
      },
      "nti āsanne samabhūmibhāge paññattaṃ therāsanena samakaṃ āsanaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ, therāsanato pana uccatare āpucchitvāpi nisīdituṃ na vaṭṭati. Yadi taṃ āsannampi nīcataraṃ hoti, anāpucchāpi nisīdituṃ vaṭṭati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mahātherasseva āpattī"
      },
      "ti āsanena paṭibāhanāpattiyā āpatti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Avattharitvā"
      },
      "ti pārutasaṅghāṭiṃ avattharitvā, anukkhipitvāti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "364.Manussānaṃparivisanaṭṭhānanti yattha antovihārepi manussā saputtadārā āvasitvā bhikkhū netvā bhojenti. Āsanesu satīti nisīdanaṭṭhānesu santesu. Idaṃ, bhante, āsanaṃ uccanti āsanne samabhūmibhāge paññattaṃ therāsanena samakaṃ āsanaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ, therāsanato pana uccatare āpucchitvāpi nisīdituṃ na vaṭṭati. Yadi taṃ āsannampi nīcataraṃ hoti, anāpucchāpi nisīdituṃ vaṭṭati. Mahātherasseva āpattīti āsanena paṭibāhanāpattiyā āpatti. Avattharitvāti pārutasaṅghāṭiṃ avattharitvā, anukkhipitvāti attho."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Pāḷiyaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘ubhohi hatthehi…pe… odano paṭiggahetabbo’’"
      },
      "ti idaṃ hatthatale vā pacchipiṭṭhiādidussaṇṭhitādhāre vā pattaṃ ṭhapetvā odanassa gahaṇakāle pattassa apatanatthāya vuttaṃ, susajjite pana ādhāre pattaṃ ṭhapetvā ekena hatthena taṃ parāmasitvāpi odanaṃ paṭiggahetuṃ vaṭṭati eva. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ubhohi hatthehi…pe… udakaṃ paṭiggahetabba"
      },
      "nti etthāpi eseva nayo."
    ],
    "innerText": "Pāḷiyaṃ ‘‘ubhohi hatthehi…pe… odano paṭiggahetabbo’’ti idaṃ hatthatale vā pacchipiṭṭhiādidussaṇṭhitādhāre vā pattaṃ ṭhapetvā odanassa gahaṇakāle pattassa apatanatthāya vuttaṃ, susajjite pana ādhāre pattaṃ ṭhapetvā ekena hatthena taṃ parāmasitvāpi odanaṃ paṭiggahetuṃ vaṭṭati eva. Ubhohi hatthehi…pe… udakaṃ paṭiggahetabbanti etthāpi eseva nayo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Hatthadhovanaudaka"
      },
      "nti bhojanāvasāne udakaṃ. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘pānīyaṃ pivitvā hatthā dhovitabbā’’"
      },
      "ti. Tena pariyosāne dhovanameva paṭikkhittaṃ, bhojanantare pana pānīyapivanādinā nayena hatthaṃ dhovitvā puna bhuñjituṃ vaṭṭatīti dasseti. Potthakesu pana ‘‘pānīyaṃ pivitvā hatthā na dhovitabbā’’ti likhanti, taṃ purimavacanena na sameti pariyosāne udakasseva ‘‘hatthadhovanaudaka’’nti vuttattā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sace manussā dhovatha, bhante"
      },
      "tiādi niṭṭhitabhattaṃ nisinnaṃ theraṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dhure"
      },
      " dvārasamīpe."
    ],
    "innerText": "Hatthadhovanaudakanti bhojanāvasāne udakaṃ. Tenāha ‘‘pānīyaṃ pivitvā hatthā dhovitabbā’’ti. Tena pariyosāne dhovanameva paṭikkhittaṃ, bhojanantare pana pānīyapivanādinā nayena hatthaṃ dhovitvā puna bhuñjituṃ vaṭṭatīti dasseti. Potthakesu pana ‘‘pānīyaṃ pivitvā hatthā na dhovitabbā’’ti likhanti, taṃ purimavacanena na sameti pariyosāne udakasseva ‘‘hatthadhovanaudaka’’nti vuttattā. Sace manussā dhovatha, bhantetiādi niṭṭhitabhattaṃ nisinnaṃ theraṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. Dhure dvārasamīpe."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Bhattaggavattakathāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Piṇḍacārikavattakathādivaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "366"
      },
      ". Pāḷiyaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ṭhāpeti vā"
      },
      "ti tiṭṭha bhanteti vadanti."
    ],
    "innerText": "366. Pāḷiyaṃ ṭhāpeti vāti tiṭṭha bhanteti vadanti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "367"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atthi, bhante, nakkhattapadānī"
      },
      "ti nakkhattapadavisayāni ñātāni atthi, assayujādinakkhattaṃ jānāthāti adhippāyo. Tenāha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘na jānāma, āvuso’’"
      },
      "ti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atthi, bhante , disābhāga"
      },
      "nti etthāpi eseva nayo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kenajja, bhante, yutta"
      },
      "nti kena nakkhattena cando yuttoti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "367.Atthi, bhante, nakkhattapadānīti nakkhattapadavisayāni ñātāni atthi, assayujādinakkhattaṃ jānāthāti adhippāyo. Tenāha ‘‘na jānāma, āvuso’’ti. Atthi, bhante , disābhāganti etthāpi eseva nayo. Kenajja, bhante, yuttanti kena nakkhattena cando yuttoti attho."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "369"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aṅgaṇe"
      },
      "ti ",
      " abbhokāse. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Evameva paṭipajjitabba"
      },
      "nti uddesadānādi āpucchitabbanti dasseti."
    ],
    "innerText": "369.Aṅgaṇeti abbhokāse. Evameva paṭipajjitabbanti uddesadānādi āpucchitabbanti dasseti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
